OL,3,CFlu hospitalisations in Wales surge as
OL,4,Ccharity issues warning
OL,6,FWales is facing a sharp increase in
OL,7,Fflu-related hospitalisations, with the
OL,8,Flatest NHS Wales figures revealing a
OL,9,F"worrying" spike in admissions.
OL,11,FIn the week ending 15 December, 195
OL,12,Fpeople were admitted to hospital due
OL,13,Fto the flu - a 44% rise compared to
OL,14,Fthe previous week, which saw 135
OL,15,Fadmissions.
