OL,3,CFlu hospitalisations in Wales surge as
OL,4,Ccharity issues warning
OL,6,FAdmissions are 3.5 times higher than
OL,7,Fthe same week last year (week ending
OL,8,F18 December 2023), when just 56 flu
OL,9,Fhospital admissions were reported,
OL,10,Faccording to the latest NHS Wales
OL,11,Fsurveillance figures.
OL,13,FIt comes as NHS Wales says they are
OL,14,F'overwhelmed' as the increase in
OL,15,Fadmissions has put added pressure on
OL,16,Fan already struggling service.
OL,18,FAs flu cases continue to rise, health
OL,19,Fexperts are urging vulnerable groups,
OL,20,Fparticularly those with lung
OL,21,Fconditions, to take extra precautions.
