OL,3,CFlu hospitalisations in Wales surge as
OL,4,Ccharity issues warning
OL,6,FAsthma + Lung UK, a leading lung
OL,7,Fcharity, has issued "vital health
OL,8,Fadvice", stressing the importance of
OL,9,Fflu vaccinations and other preventive
OL,10,Fmeasures.
OL,12,FThe charity has expressed particular
OL,13,Fconcern for people with asthma,
OL,14,Fchronic obstructive pulmonary disease
OL,15,F(COPD), and other respiratory
OL,16,Fconditions, who are at heightened risk
OL,17,Fof serious complications from the flu.
