OL,3,CFlu hospitalisations in Wales surge as
OL,4,Ccharity issues warning
OL,6,FIn a statement, Joseph Carter, Head of
OL,7,FAsthma + Lung UK Cymru, said: "It's
OL,8,Freally worrying that flu admissions
OL,9,Fare rising week on week in Wales. It's
OL,10,Fcrucial that people with lung
OL,11,Fconditions protect themselves by
OL,12,Fgetting their free flu vaccine if they
OL,13,Fare eligible.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/9
