OL,3,CFlu hospitalisations in Wales surge as
OL,4,Ccharity issues warning
OL,6,F"This winter, people with lung
OL,7,Fconditions face a triple threat of
OL,8,Fflu, COVID-19 and respiratory
OL,9,Fsyncytial virus (RSV). For some people
OL,10,Fwith lung conditions, being exposed to
OL,11,Fany of these, or a combination, can
OL,12,Fcause a flare-up of symptoms and make
OL,13,Fthem more vulnerable to illnesses."
OL,15,FHe added that those with asthma could
OL,16,Fface life-threatening complications
OL,17,Fand hospitalisation should they
OL,18,Fcontract the flu.
