OL,3,CFlu hospitalisations in Wales surge as
OL,4,Ccharity issues warning
OL,6,F"We also want people with asthma and
OL,7,FCOPD to make sure they are taking
OL,8,Ftheir medicines as prescribed,
OL,9,Fincluding using their preventer
OL,10,Finhaler daily even when they feel
OL,11,Fwell, as this builds up protection in
OL,12,Ftheir airways over time, and carrying
OL,13,Ftheir reliever inhaler with them. It
OL,14,Fis also a good idea to avoid contact
OL,15,Fwith people who have cold or flu
OL,16,Fsymptoms.", he said.
