OL,3,CFlu hospitalisations in Wales surge as
OL,4,Ccharity issues warning
OL,6,FWith the festive season fast
OL,7,Fapproaching, public health officials
OL,8,Fare reminding people to remain
OL,9,Fvigilant and take steps to prevent the
OL,10,Fspread of flu, including hand hygiene,
OL,11,Fmask-wearing, and staying home if
OL,12,Funwell.
