OL,3,CFlu hospitalisations in Wales surge as
OL,4,Ccharity issues warning
OL,6,FResponding to the 'unrelenting demand'
OL,7,Fon the health service, director of the
OL,8,FWelsh NHS Confederation Darren Hughes
OL,9,Fsaid: "We know in recent weeks the
OL,10,Fnumber of people hospitalised with flu
OL,11,Fhas been rising, which, alongside
OL,12,Fhigher levels of Covid, RSV and
OL,13,FNorovirus in the winter months, puts
OL,14,Fmounting pressure on services.
