OL,3,CFlu hospitalisations in Wales surge as
OL,4,Ccharity issues warning
OL,6,FHe continued: "NHS organisations have
OL,7,Fput a range of urgent and emergency
OL,8,Fcare interventions in place, including
OL,9,Frapid clinical screening of 999
OL,10,Fcallers and additional Community
OL,11,FWelfare Responders trained to attend
OL,12,Fappropriate 999 calls in their
OL,13,Fcommunity. Cwm Taf Morgannwg UHB has,
OL,14,Ffor example, created a Navigation Hub
OL,15,Fto reduce conveyances to emergency
OL,16,Fdepartments, treating and remotely
OL,17,Fmonitoring patients in their own home
OL,18,Fwhere appropriate."
